    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:1.2",
          "pli": "“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattanti. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, when these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:1.3",
          "pli": "Katame aṭṭha? ",
          "en": "What eight? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:1.4",
          "pli": "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. ",
          "en": "They are right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:1.5",
          "pli": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattantī”ti. ",
          "en": "When these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:2.1",
          "pli": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
          "en": "That is what the Buddha said. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:2.2",
          "pli": "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: ",
          "en": "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:3.1",
          "pli": "“Appakā te manussesu, ",
          "en": "“Few are those among humans "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:3.2",
          "pli": "ye janā pāragāmino; ",
          "en": "who cross to the far shore. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:3.3",
          "pli": "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā, ",
          "en": "The rest just run "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:3.4",
          "pli": "tīramevānudhāvati. ",
          "en": "around on the near shore. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:4.1",
          "pli": "Ye ca kho sammadakkhāte, ",
          "en": "When the teaching is well explained, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:4.2",
          "pli": "dhamme dhammānuvattino; ",
          "en": "those who practice accordingly "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:4.3",
          "pli": "Te janā pāramessanti, ",
          "en": "are the ones who will cross over "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:4.4",
          "pli": "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ. ",
          "en": "Death’s domain so hard to pass. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:5.1",
          "pli": "Kaṇhaṃ dhammaṃ vippahāya, ",
          "en": "Rid of dark qualities, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:5.2",
          "pli": "sukkaṃ bhāvetha paṇḍito; ",
          "en": "an astute person should develop the bright. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:5.3",
          "pli": "Okā anokamāgamma, ",
          "en": "Leaving home behind "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:5.4",
          "pli": "viveke yattha dūramaṃ. ",
          "en": "for the seclusion so hard to enjoy, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:6.1",
          "pli": "Tatrābhiratimiccheyya, ",
          "en": "you should try to find delight there, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:6.2",
          "pli": "hitvā kāme akiñcano; ",
          "en": "having left behind sensual pleasures. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:6.3",
          "pli": "Pariyodapeyya attānaṃ, ",
          "en": "With no possessions, an astute person "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:6.4",
          "pli": "cittaklesehi paṇḍito. ",
          "en": "should cleanse themselves of mental corruptions. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.1",
          "pli": "Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu, ",
          "en": "And those whose minds are rightly developed "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.2",
          "pli": "sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ; ",
          "en": "in the awakening factors; "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.3",
          "pli": "Ādānapaṭinissagge, ",
          "en": "letting go of attachments, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.4",
          "pli": "anupādāya ye ratā; ",
          "en": "they delight in not grasping. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.5",
          "pli": "Khīṇāsavā jutimanto, ",
          "en": "With defilements ended, brilliant, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.6",
          "pli": "te loke parinibbutā”ti. ",
          "en": "they are extinguished in this world.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.34:7.7",
          "pli": "Catutthaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
